<title>CANADA: QUALITY - Lufthansa Canada June cargo report.</title>
<headline>QUALITY - Lufthansa Canada June cargo report.</headline>
<dateline>TORONTO 1997-07-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Lufthansa Cargo AG 's latest monthly report on service standards at its Canadian gateways, Montreal, Toronto and Vancouver in percent compared to May 1977 shows</p>
<p>    Customer commitment   Achievement</p>
<p>    June 1997		   May 1997</p>
<p>Flown as booked</p>
<p>(Confirmed bookings within six hour time frame)</p>
<p>    93.20			95.40</p>
<p>Telephone accessibility</p>
<p>(Incoming calls answered within 25 seconds, or four rings)</p>
<p>    91			   93.83</p>
<p>Documents availability</p>
<p>(General cargo, passenger flights, within four hours of arrival)</p>
<p>    100			 100</p>
<p>(General cargo, freighter flights, within five hours of arrival)</p>
<p>    100			 100</p>
<p>(Express cargo, available within 1.5 hours of arrival)</p>
<p>    100			 100</p>
<p>Truck waiting time</p>
<p>(maximum 30 minutes between arrival and unloading)</p>
<p>    100t			100</p>
<p>Booking confirmation</p>
<p>(Reply within two hours)</p>
<p>    98.8			 98.1</p>
<p>Claims handling</p>
<p>(preliminary response within seven days)</p>
<p>    100			 100</p>
<p>(Final settlement within four weeks)</p>
<p>    100			 100</p>
<p>- Reuters Air Cargo Service Tel+ 44 171 542 7706 Fax +5017 - www.racs.com</p>
